    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白，INIT作为初始状态很清晰。那INIT之后应该进入什么状态？是直接进入数据传输吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "INIT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "不，中间要有个HANDSHAKING阶段。当LabAnalyzer连接上来时，触发on_connected事件，从INIT转到HANDSHAKING。这个握手阶段很重要，要验证设备身份。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "INIT",
        "HANDSHAKING",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "on_connected"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画出了INIT到HANDSHAKING的转换，标注了on_connected和LabAnalyzer。那握手完成后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "INIT",
        "HANDSHAKING",
        "on_connected",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "握手成功后进入STREAMING状态。这里有两个触发条件：on_first_data来自LabAnalyzer的首包数据，同时EMR_Sync要发心跳on_heartbeat。这两个条件都满足才能进入正式流传输。",
